task.summary: Create basic data structure to save matrix dataset. Create dataset loader to load data from file.
Implemented linear regression with stochastic gradient.

1. Implemented zero mean unit variance normalization. 2. Finished Linear Regression on boston housing dataset (test mse: 21) 3. Implemented validation to calculate MSE. 4. Added some handy method to set and get value in matrix.
1. Implemented logistic regression. 2. Implemented Confusion Matrix. 3. Added new dataset Spambase. 4. Added split and shuffle method in Matrix
Implemented K-Fold Cross Validation on spambase dataset.

Implemented Binary Decision Tree. 1. Created abstract Cart for common logic shared by decision tree and regression tree. 2. Implemented decision tree. 3. Tested spambase with 10 fold cross validation on decision tree. 4. Added split method in Matrix using Predicate.
